⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Peter Parkette
node LMM · LMM · ⟦Peter Parkette:LMM:c04900⟧

WHO   — Peter Parkette — the boy who saw him human
WHAT  — The innocence the story is measured against: the one who liked Jobe before he was useful or terrifying.
WHERE — LMM · The Lawnmower Man (1992)  Framework inputs: The Lawnmower Man (1992, dir. Brett Leonard, New Line); verified cast & facts  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the tragedy needs a witness to the kindness being lost, and Peter is it.
HOW   — By being Jobe's friend throughout, and grieving the person the experiment erased.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  He used to let me ride on the mower. I knew him before they made him smart. I'm the one who remembers he was kind.

